        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Larva of P. saohimea sp. n. a-b. Shape variation in sternal spatula and associated papillae; c. Dorsal view of 8 th and terminal abdominal segments. Scale bars = 50 µm." , "Figure 5. Scanning electron micrographs of pupa of Pseudasphondylia saohimea sp. n. a. Ventral view of head b. Prothoracic spiracle; c. Lateral view of abdominal segments. Scale bars = 50 µm." , "Figure 2. Pseudasphondylia saohimea sp. n. a. Head; b. Female flagellomere V. c. Male flagellomere V; d. General shape of female flagellomeres; e. General shape of male flagellomeres; f. Male flagellomeres X-XII; g. Wing; h. Acromere of fore-leg. i. Acromere of hind-leg. Scale bars = 50 µm." , "Figure 3. Pseudasphondylia saohimea sp. n. a. Terminal part of female abdomen; b. Male terminalia. Scale bars = 50 µm." , "Figure 6. Maximum Likelihood phylogenetic tree of Japanese Pseudasphondylia species, based on a fragment of COI. Bootstrap values are indicated for nodes that gained> 50 % support in 1,000 replications." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531575" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531422" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531579" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531580" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531577" .

